text: Uhtred was the King of Hwicce, jointly with Eanberht and Ealdred. In 757 Eanberht, Uhtred, and Ealdred, granted land to Bishop Milred, and in 759 to Abbot Headda. In 770 Uhtred issued a charter to his thegn Æthelmund. Another grant, to thegn Coelmund, is dated 756, apparently in error for 777, 778, or 779. == References == ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:Hwiccan monarchs Category:8th-century English monarchs
